{"tid":1632032,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實裝修私了根本唔係問題 唔需要割","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:24.000Z","uid":89353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a56c902adeec6e6dbff1c7f7957c86537b6593","tid":1632032,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"你哋可能話我哋裝修好開心所以不不停做<br />\n但裝修係有佢嘅意義<br />\n係對<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色資本</span>、中共用商家權力剝削人民嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代價</span></span><br />\n而私了係<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">以暴制暴</span></span>嘅一種方法<br />\n<br />\n所以只要對準目標<br />\n冇對錯人嘅話<br />\n根本冇問題<br />\n<br />\n當然如果只係獅子狗<br />\n話你幾句私了係唔公道<br />\n對錯公司裝修係唔公義<br />\n<br />\n不過都係果句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不完美但可以接受可以改進</span></span><br />\n都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔可以割席</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">對準政權<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></div>"},{"pid":"63e4dd251352e163ed98bee6416af34ec8eccc9f","tid":1632032,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:51.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ef0cf966b270e2a086feebd83f597279bc7290c2","tid":1632032,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"外媒中立報導 冇惡意抹黑<br />\n成堆弱智仔衝出黎話外國唔鍾意<br />\n係唔係一日就會令香港人權問題消失唔需要解決？因為裝修所以冇左人權問題？"}]}